open mind that's guided by fact and logic, rather than ideology. He
is also a compassionate man.''
   Connecticut's presidential primary is March 29. Bush is
considered the favorite in the GOP contest in Connecticut because
he grew up in the state, his father was a U.S. senator from
Connecticut and his mother and brother still live in Greenwich.
