<TEXT>
   WASHINGTON (APents.
   ``You find me a professor anywhere in North America that can
handle 3,169 questions _ and they weren't stupid questions,''
Phillips said.
   Students who miss Phillips' lecture on the first day of class
can only guess at the appearance of the professor known by his
computer address ``gmp.''
   ``One says she's going to track me down to see what I look like
and talk to me face to face. I said `Catch me if you can,''' said
Phillips.
   One student who asked that her name not be used said the course
