La.; 27 at Little Rock, Ark.; 27 at Macon, Ga.; 20 at Mena, Ark.;25
at Memphis, Tenn.; 20 at Meridian, Miss.; 27 at Mobile, Ala.; 26 at
Monroe, La.; 25 at Montgomery, Ala.; 40 at New Orleans, tie; 30 at
