15.09 points to 2,050.07.
   The dollar was mixed against other major currencies. Gold prices
edged higher.
   Bond prices finished mixed in lackluster trading.
   Soybean futures prices soared as fears about increased soybean
acreage eased. Grain futures also closed higher.
</TEXT>
