to 116 and IBM was down 1] to 114[.
   Auto stocks were mostly lower. Chrysler was down \ to 24[, Ford
was down ] to 43~ and General Motors fell [ to 71|. The major
automakers reported mostly mixed results for the early March sales
period.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks fell
0.21 to 149.85. At the American Stock Exchange, the market value
index was down 0.70 at 296.24.
