<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Stock prices were little changed today in light,
lackluster trading.
   Analysts said the market drifted in a narrow range as both
institutional and retail investors remained on the sidelines while
awaiting fresh economic news due out later in the week.
   The government is scheduled to release January's merchandise
